Create backup from golden/config root folder: tar czf unvback-demo-state.tar.gz .tmp/data.db public/uploads
On the remote server:
git clone https://github.com/ORG/unvback.git
cd unvback
cp .env.example .env   # then fill secrets (or use team vault)
npm ci
npm run build
